data.description: Ask about seller credits for rate buy down, closing costs etc. Welcome to 63 Scotts Dr. in the desirable Spence Creek subdivision. Experience the modern kitchen with sleek stainless steel appliances, overlooking the oversized back yard and living space. Retreat to the exquisite master suite, offering a private oasis for relaxation. The versatile bonus room adds flexibility, allowing you to customize it as a home office, gym, or playroom. The large fenced back yard is perfect for outdoor activities and entertaining. Enjoy the community amenities, including playgrounds, walking trails, a clubhouse and amazing pool. With some of the most highly rated schools in the state,  convenient shopping, dining, and entertainment options nearby, this house has it ALL. Make 63 Scotts Dr. your DREAM HOME today! (Buyer’s agent to verify all pertinent information)
